item.title: WAM Partners Website Proposal
item.description: During my time at WAM Partners I was able to work on a side project that involved the company. I was able to create a website using WordPress with a custom theme using Advanced Custom Fields (ACF) in the back end, and then using Bootstrap for the front end. Listings Website Problem So the initial problem I had run into while working at WAM Partners was having to update their website.
